rc= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/a5750928-cb9b-4308-8144-36fb91f5ff72.png\"/> mà:\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/f58c615f-e4c4-410f-84b5-a66020a792c7.png\"/> là trung điểm <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/6bcf9bfc-2e5d-423b-a6e9-41535f19fa58.png\"/> (do GT);\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/1fa1ea6d-787f-4186-83d7-9ceb9bd15e40.png\"/> là trung điểm <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/bbfa3fa5-011c-467e-8562-b3953ac5cd06.png\"/> (do <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/7e452d81-cea4-49df-b5fe-0655b77ef03c.png\"/>)\n<br>Suy ra tứ giác <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/da80664b-4d13-4aa3-83dc-61ce46b10cbb.png\"/> là hình bình hành\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/ab4caa45-2baf-4b26-a102-8f9b9c6c00b6.png\"/> (cạnh đối hình bình hành)\n<br>Ta có: <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/257b37b4-553f-409a-a4b4-0e26388a7adf.png\"/> (cùng vuông góc với <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/1b6e6ccf-328e-4afc-9ca5-186e4a4bb4db.png\"/>) và <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/884b2455-a3e4-4c23-a82e-92491bc7df21.png\"/> nên 3 điểm <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/12/081c41fb-ebdb-40f8-965e-d202b1826837.png\"/> thẳng hàng (theo tiên đề Euclid).\n",
